## Context routing — `/fl <task>`
Trước khi sửa/dev → gọi:
```
/fl <mô tả task>
```
→ Spawn `context-router` agent → output ordered list `.md` cần đọc + pre-flight flags.

Agent: `.claude/agents/context-router.md`. Slash: `.claude/commands/fl.md`.

